// This file defines all special_functions operators via X-macro.
// Each REGISTER_OP(name, arity, impl) entry is expanded by the including file.
//
// Arity: number of input Tensor arguments to the forward function.
// impl: unused placeholder for future per-operator customization.
//
// Excluded: log_multivariate_gamma (non-standard int parameter)

